      "rationale": "Only two mesh densities were evaluated (coarse and medium); formal Richardson extrapolation and GCI calculation were not performed. The medium mesh was selected based on visual inspection of velocity contours rather than quantitative convergence criteria. Discretization error for the hemolysis index QoI remains uncharacterised and potentially significant given the high shear-stress sensitivity of the power-law hemolysis model employed."
