    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concluded that the CFD model achieves High assurance for the CPB hemolysis COU. Six of seven assessed factors meet or exceed their required levels, and six factors were appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions and supporting the 510(k) comparative hemolysis submission.",
